name: Crypto Currency Mining Bot
desc: Crypto mining for Duino Coin involves using hashing algorithms to solve complex mathematical problems, contributing to the secure verification and validation of transactions within the blockchain network, while earning rewards in the form of Duino Coins.

name: Online Movie Ticket Booking System
desc: The movie ticket booking system project is a software application that enables users to browse movie listings, select seats, and book tickets online, streamlining the ticketing process and providing a convenient platform for moviegoers to secure their seats in advance. Devolped Using HTML, CSS, JS, PHP

name: On Road Fuel Delivery
desc: The on-road fuel delivery Android application allows users to conveniently request fuel delivery to their location, eliminating the need to visit a gas station. With just a few taps, users can have fuel delivered directly to their vehicles, saving time and providing a hassle-free refueling experience.

name: Queue Operation visualisation
desc: The queue operation visualization using computer graphics creates a graphical representation of a queue data structure, showcasing the enqueue and dequeue operations. This interactive visual display helps users understand the sequential nature of the queue and how elements are added and removed in a first-in-first-out manner.
